<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head><%- include('../partials/head', { title }) %></head>
<body class="page-about">
<%- include('../partials/header', { activePage }) %>

<main class="about-main">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero-blob" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container about-hero-inner">
      <h1>About moovex</h1>
      <p class="about-lead">
        A catalyst for Zambian innovation, bridging the gap between local potential and global opportunity.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-commitment">
    <div class="container about-commitment-inner">
      <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
      <p>
        moovex Zambia stands at the forefront of the nation's entrepreneurial revolution. We are more than a single
        business—we are a non-profit organization and dedicated ecosystem builder committed to fostering sustainable
        growth, practical business systems, and stronger local enterprise. By empowering visionary Zambian entrepreneurs
        with guidance, networks, mentorship, and practical business support, we ensure that the next generation of
        industry leaders has the tools to thrive in Zambia's connected entrepreneurship ecosystem.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-mission-vision">
    <div class="container about-mv-grid">
      <article class="about-card about-soft-shadow">
        <div class="about-card-icon about-card-icon-orange" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M14.4 6L14 4H5v17h2v-7h5.6l.4 2h7V6h-5.6z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>
          To promote entrepreneurship in Zambia by helping companies grow through guidance, networks, practical systems,
          and business collaboration across the moovex ecosystem.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="about-card about-soft-shadow">
        <div class="about-card-icon about-card-icon-green" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 4.5C7 4.5 2.73 7.61 1 12c1.73 4.39 6 7.5 11 7.5s9.27-3.11 11-7.5c-1.73-4.39-6-7.5-11-7.5zM12 17c-2.76 0-5-2.24-5-5s2.24-5 5-5 5 2.24 5 5-2.24 5-5 5zm0-8c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3 3-1.34 3-3-1.34-3-3-3z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Our Vision</h3>
        <p>
          A vibrant, connected Zambian economy where entrepreneurs build sustainable companies that create meaningful
          employment, improve local services, and serve communities across the country.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-what-we-do">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <div class="about-do-list">
        <article class="about-do-item">
          <div class="about-do-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M11.8 10.9c-2.27-.59-3-1.2-3-2.15 0-1.09 1.01-1.85 2.7-1.85 1.78 0 2.44.85 2.5 2.1h2.21c-.07-1.72-1.12-3.3-3.21-3.81V3h-3v2.16c-1.94.42-3.5 1.68-3.5 3.61 0 2.31 1.91 3.46 4.7 4.13 2.5.6 3 1.48 3 2.41 0 .69-.49 1.79-2.7 1.79-2.06 0-2.87-.92-2.98-2.1h-2.2c.12 2.19 1.76 3.42 3.68 3.83V21h3v-2.15c1.95-.37 3.5-1.5 3.5-3.55 0-2.84-2.43-3.81-4.7-4.4z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4>Strategic Support</h4>
            <p>Providing practical guidance and entrepreneurship support to high-growth potential startups.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="about-do-item">
          <div class="about-do-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M22 11V3h-7v3H9V3H2v8h7V8h2v10h4v3h7v-8h-7v3h-2V8h2v3h7z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4>Ecosystem Integration</h4>
            <p>Building bridges between entrepreneurs, government bodies, and international partners.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="about-do-item">
          <div class="about-do-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 6h18V4H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h14v-2H4V6zm13 6H9v2h8v-2zm0-4H9v2h8V8zM4 8h2v2H4V8zm15 8h-4v2h4v-2zM4 12h2v2H4v-2zm11 4H9v2h6v-2z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4>Digital Transformation</h4>
            <p>Empowering traditional businesses with modern digital tools and infrastructure.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="about-do-item">
          <div class="about-do-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16 11c1.66 0 3-1.34 3-3s-1.34-3-3-3-3 1.34-3 3 1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 3-1.34 3-3S9.66 5 8 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5C15 14.17 10.33 13 8 13zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4>Mentorship &amp; Support</h4>
            <p>Hands-on guidance from industry veterans to navigate growth and operations.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-values">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
      <div class="about-values-grid">
        <article class="about-value-card">
          <div class="about-value-icon about-value-icon-green" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2.5l2.2 6.8H21l-5.5 4 2.1 6.7L12 16.8 6.4 20l2.1-6.7L3 9.3h6.8L12 2.5z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Entrepreneurship</h3>
        </article>

        <article class="about-value-card">
          <div class="about-value-icon about-value-icon-teal" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Collaboration</h3>
        </article>

        <article class="about-value-card">
          <div class="about-value-icon about-value-icon-orange" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l1.8 5.5H19l-4.6 3.3 1.8 5.5L12 13l-4.2 3.3 1.8-5.5L5 7.5h5.2L12 2z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Impact</h3>
        </article>

        <article class="about-value-card">
          <div class="about-value-icon about-value-icon-blue" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm-2 16l-4-4 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l6.59-6.59L18 9l-8 8z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Integrity</h3>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-why-zambia">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-photo-card">
        <div
          class="about-photo about-photo-zambia"
          role="img"
          aria-label="A vibrant, busy street market in Lusaka, Zambia, at dusk with golden hour lighting"
        ></div>
        <div class="about-photo-overlay"></div>
        <div class="about-photo-content">
          <h2>Why Zambia?</h2>
          <p>
            Zambia is home to a burgeoning population of young, tech-savvy creators. However, the gap in structured
            support and practical business systems remains a barrier. moovex is here to bridge that gap, turning local
            talent into connected enterprise.
          </p>
          <a href="/partner" class="about-btn about-btn-primary">Join the Movement</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
<script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
